DateTime::Locale::en_Shaw(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::en_Shaw(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::en_Shaw

SYNOPSIS

  use DateTime;

  my $dt = DateTime->now( locale => 'en_Shaw' );
  print $dt->month_name();

DESCRIPTION

This is the DateTime locale package for English Shavian.

DATA

This locale inherits from the DateTime::Locale::en locale.

It contains the following data.

Date Formats

Full

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = XXXXXXXXX 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = XXXXXXXX 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = XXXXXXXXX 15, -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = XXX 5, 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = XXX 22, 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = XXX 15, -10

Available Formats

d (d)

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 XXX
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 XXX
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 XXX
